Disney  will start streaming  Frozen 2  on Sunday  three months early,In a move that feels in parts altruistic and business savvy  Disney has bumped up the Disney  streaming release date for Frozen 2 to this weekend  Many families are unexpectedly home and certainly feeling the stress of everything going on due to coronavirus  ,The press release didn t indicate exactly what time Frozen 2 will premiere on Disney  but said it will be available only in HD initially  and only in the US  Starting Tuesday March 17th  it will also come to Canada  the Netherlands  Australia and New Zealand  380 chars 
